title: Jailhouse rock: BJP now joins in, Azam guest list grows longer - The Indian Express
content: Jailhouse rock: BJP now joins in, Azam guest list grows longer  The Indian Express
description: After RLD leader Jayant Chaudhary and Pragatisheel Samajwadi Party leader Shivpal Singh Yadav visited him in prison, Azam has now received a Congress guest, and, the biggest surprise of all, praise from the BJP.
